entity.description: Post-tropical cyclone Dorian, which has already damaged or destroyed thousands of homes in the Bahamas and claimed at least 43 lives, made landfall near Halifax on Saturday evening.

data.text: This is it Sofla! We’ll start to feel some of #HurricaneDorian as early as late tonight, if you’re not seeing strong wind already. @CBS12 will have crews ALL around our area, and I will be covering from @CityPortStLucie! Everyone stay safe, and pray for the Bahamas.
